We offer cleaning services for commercial, residential, Airbnb, post construction, post renovations, move-in and move-out cleans. Commercial buildings, schools, churches, medical facilities, office buildings, and more.

profile:
Absolutely Spotless Cleaning was founded by Jennifer Bell in 2007. Having trained as a professional house cleaner for 5 years prior to opening Absolutely Spotless, she now proudly offers over 18 years experience in cleaning homes and apartments/condos of all sizes. Our commitment to customer service is evident by the number of our many satisfied customers throughout the Durham Region and Burlington/Oakville region and references and reviews of our services are available.

We offer professional, detailed cleaning of the highest standard. One time, regular, occasional, move-in/out cleans, post renovation cleans available. Partial cleans available. Insured and bonded for your protection. Servicing all of Durham Region and surrounding areas, as well as Hamilton, Burlington, Oakville, Ancaster, Brantford and all surrounding areas. 

Absolutely Spotless Cleaning is registered and carries business insurance for your peace of mind and protection. Employees are covered by WSIB and government employee taxes are remitted.

profile:
SteriGleam Janitorial Corp. is a commercial cleaning company providing custodian services to office spaces, medical health centres, dental clinics, pharmacies, retail stores, and apartment buildings. While other companies clean, we offer value to our customers by incorporating modern laboratory and medical sterilization and sanitation procedures within our processes.

All of our staff continually trains in the latest compliance methods and are insured and bonded. In addition to our janitorial services, we provide third-party sterilization compliance testing through adenosine triphosphate (ATP) bioluminescence measurements, laboratory pathogen surface analysis, and quality medical and janitorial supplies from national vendors.

We have over 15 years of experience in maintaining intensive care units, operating rooms, emergency departments, and medical analysis clinics.

profile:
As residential cleaning experts we take pride in every home we service.
All products used are safe for your family,pets and the environment. 

As a mom of 2 I’ve been cleaning houses and small businesses for over 16 years and have been successfully running A Cleaning By B's for just over 4 years on my own and absolutely love what I do. The most rewarding part of my job is when clients return home from a long day of work and send me a txt or email saying how happy they are and how clean their home is.. 

Our goal is to clean your home from top to bottom and give you more time to do the things you enjoy. 

Contact us today for a free, no-obligation in-home estimate of your house cleaning needs.

My sister is a licensed vet tech at a veterinarian clinic and lets me know if the cleaners I'm using are safe for your pets I also use a Bissel pet pro vacuum that has a volume button that allows me to lower the sound of the vacuum so pets and small children that are home aren’t easily scared it also all comes apart and at the end of each day and its all washed and disinfected for the next day of cleaning all mop heads are numbered to your house key and the mop head you have is only used in your home and at the next house the mop head comes off and a new one is put on same with all clothes and rags. we use color-coordinated clothes. green clothes are only used in bathrooms and grey ones are only used in the kitchens.. all Swiffer dusters are thrown out at the end of each clean at each home and new ones are put on for the next home/next clean.. we are so dedicated to paying attention to detail especially during this time in a worldwide pandemic.. we hope by you allowing us into your homes we can meet all your cleaning needs and then some. hope to talk to you soon from us all at A Cleaning By B's.
